data.description: This lovely 3 bedroom 2 bath home in Luckey Ranch is ready for new owners! You will enjoy the open floor plan, complete with a spacious living room, eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar and tile flooring, primary bedroom with full bath, and well-sized secondary bedrooms.  The exterior boast a side deck, privacy fence, storage shed and energy efficient solar panels. Conveniently located nearby Luckey Ranch Subdivision Park.  Don't miss this opportunity to make this your next home, book your personal tour today!
